OL,3,CAnger as new bus gate fines earn city
OL,4,Ccouncil #500k in three months
OL,6,FA new bus gate in has netted the city
OL,7,Fcouncil more than half a million
OL,8,Fpounds in less than three months, new
OL,9,Ffigures reveal.
OL,11,FThe Cumberland Road bus gate only
OL,12,Fbegan charging in January but has
OL,13,Falready faced heavy criticism from
OL,14,Fcampaigners.
OL,16,FA bus gate is a stretch of road only
OL,17,Fopen to buses, black cabs and cyclists
OL,18,Fand is generally shorter than a bus
OL,19,Flane.
