OL,3,CAnger as new bus gate fines earn city
OL,4,Ccouncil #500k in three months
OL,6,FBristol City Council says it was
OL,7,Fbrought in to improve air quality and
OL,8,Fgive priority to buses travelling into
OL,9,Fthe city centre.
OL,11,FIt says 14 signs have been installed
OL,12,Fnear the gate to warn drivers, as well
OL,13,Fas clear road markings.
OL,15,FHowever some residents claim the signs
OL,16,Fare not easy to spot and end up
OL,17,F'punishing' unaware motorists.
