OL,3,CAnger as new bus gate fines earn city
OL,4,Ccouncil #500k in three months
OL,6,FAccording to figures released by
OL,7,FBristol City Council under the Freedom
OL,8,Fof Information Act, between 2 January
OL,9,Fwhen the camera became active and 19
OL,10,FMarch, 22,366 fines were issued
OL,11,Ftotalling #513,369.
OL,13,FThis would mean that, in theory, the
OL,14,Flocal authority is on course to earn
OL,15,F#4m by the end of the year.
OL,17,FBristol Bus Gate campaigner Matt
OL,18,FSanders says he is angered by the
OL,19,Fcouncil's scheme, which he claims is
OL,20,F"simply not correct".
