OL,3,CAnger as new bus gate fines earn city
OL,4,Ccouncil #500k in three months
OL,6,F"I haven't actually been caught here
OL,7,Fmyself", said Matt, who is a TV set
OL,8,Fdesigner and art director for Aardman.
OL,10,F"I was caught at one in a different
OL,11,Fpart of the country a year or so back,
OL,12,Fso I started reading up all the rules
OL,13,Fand regulations for signage and design
OL,14,Fof bus gates."
OL,16,F"I thought I couldn't stand by and see
OL,17,Fthis carry on when I know for a fact a
OL,18,Flot of it simply isn't correct."
