OL,3,CAnger as new bus gate fines earn city
OL,4,Ccouncil #500k in three months
OL,6,FMatt says a number of his colleagues
OL,7,Fhave been fined after driving through
OL,8,Fthe gate - some up to eleven times, he
OL,9,Ftold ITV News.
OL,11,F"Because your letter doesn't come for
OL,12,Fthe first couple of weeks, and in the
OL,13,Fmean time you might have gone through
OL,14,Fseveral more times by mistake", he
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,F"In a normal bus lane the bus lane is
OL,18,Fon the left and other cars can drive
OL,19,Fnext to it. On a bus gate nobody is
OL,20,Fallowed to go that way at all unless
OL,21,Fthey're a bus or a taxi or a bicycle.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
