OL,3,CAnger as new bus gate fines earn city
OL,4,Ccouncil #500k in three months
OL,6,F"So they have to have an escape route,
OL,7,Fin this situation the last junction
OL,8,Fbefore the bus gate is Gas Ferry Road
OL,9,Fwhich is actually a no through road so
OL,10,Fthat can't be an escape route.
OL,12,F"You have to realise sixty metres
OL,13,Fbefore the Bus Gate you have to turn
OL,14,Fleft, and the sign which tells you to
OL,15,Fdo that is way too small for a 30 mph
OL,16,Froad."
OL,18,FHowever the city council says red road
OL,19,Fsurfacing is in place in the area, as
OL,20,Fwell as 14 warning signs, to enhance
OL,21,Fthe visibility of the gate.
