OL,3,CAnger as new bus gate fines earn city
OL,4,Ccouncil #500k in three months
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Bristol City
OL,7,FCouncil said: "The bus gate on
OL,8,FCumberland Road was installed to help
OL,9,Fimprove air quality and give priority
OL,10,Fto buses travelling into the city
OL,11,Fcentre.
OL,13,F"National government regulations only
OL,14,Frequire councils to display two signs
OL,15,Ffor a bus gate, but we have installed
OL,16,F14 signs in the area for this one
OL,17,Falongside clear 'bus gate' road
OL,18,Fmarkings.
