OL,6,F"To give extra warning, an electronic
OL,7,Fsign was put in place for a month
OL,8,Fshortly after the bus gate was
OL,9,Finstalled in September 2023.
OL,11,F"People who continued to drive through
OL,12,Fthis bus gate in error were issued
OL,13,Fwith warning letters as a reminder,
OL,14,Fbefore the first Penalty Charge
OL,15,FNotices were issued four months later
OL,16,Fin January 2024.
